content_text:
State of the Project: DexCheck weekly development update
#10
We are connecting the dots that create smarter investors and boost investment success. Each week, we share our efforts and progress towards this goal. We are committed to keeping our community informed on what goes on behind the scenes. As the market continues on the path of recovery, we are honing the tools in our ecosystem and building new ones according to what is required in the dynamic crypto market.
We are diversifying and moving deeper into DeFAI and InfoFi as a tooling mechanism for crypto investors. This week, we made significant progress.
Hereâ€™s the 10th edition of our weekly development update
Â» Attention Index: Following the launch of the Attention Index tab and associated features, we are reviewing the performance in Prod. and deploying fixes where needed. We are also studying user behaviour to ensure that the tool meets the user's requirements. This week, we integrated the â€˜overall mentionsâ€™ parameter to the tab to present further information on social activity for featured tokens. We also added data on real-time changes in holder count.
Â» Dexplore: Our blockchain search engine continues to get smarter and faster. The training process continues as we add more information to the modelâ€™s library and optimize the performance for faster inferences. We fixed critical bugs and also modified the UI for a better outlook and experience.
Â» CHECK: This week, we announced CHECK, a progressive reward system for X users contributing to important discussions. Development is already underway for the platform! We hope to share more information on this in subsequent updates.
Â» Liquidity Boost on Pancakeswap: The $DCK token is native to
@BNBCHAIN
and tradable on
@pancakeSwap
. This week, we added more assets to the tune of $100,000 to the DCK/BUSD pair.
Â» KOL Tracker and Performance Index: We updated the logic for the KOL tracker and performance index to enable the algorithm to track posts without cash tags. This will significantly improve the accuracy of information generated by both tools.
Â» New integrations: We completed integrations for
@pumpdotfun
â€™s new AMM. Users can now track activity on the protocol via DexCheck.
Â» UI Improvements: We also improved the platformâ€™s design in key areas to adjust to best design practices and improve user experience. Youâ€™ll notice major changes in the outlook of the Wallet Analyzer and Token Analytics tools.
Â» Address Tagging: We are adding labels to unique wallets for identification. This week, we deprecated the old tagging system, tested the new tagging script for Ethereum addresses, and added PnL-based tags for BNB Chain addresses. We also added tags Tron and Ton network addresses.
Â» Optimizations for existing tools: We are working on major updates for InsightsGPT/ Smart Traders Moves. We are also integrating new changes for Wallet Analyzer across every network supported on the platform.
DexCheck is designed to bring out the best in every trader. With every update and launch, this statement becomes even more realistic. This month, we launched two primary features and several add-ons to existing tools. In the coming week and month, we will continue in this direction and evolve according to usersâ€™ and market demand.

â¥ BNB Chain's Pascal Hardfork upgrade.
BNB Chainâ€™s successful implementation of EIP-7702 through the Pascal Hardfork improved the EVM compatibility & introduced Gasless transactions, Batch approvals & swaps in one click Easier.
This upgrade was pivotal for the onboarding and adoption of the chain, evident on the 7D DEX volume chart.
BNB Chainâ€™s roadmap doesnâ€™t stop here, btw.

#MUBARAK
This month, Binance announced that it had received a $2 billion investment from the Arab sovereign fund MGX, this led to an Arab cartoon inspired meme â€œMubarakâ€ which was quoted by CZ.
This move unexpectedly promoted the steady rise in the price of the newly born meme coin Mubarak on the 13th.
â¥ The BNB Chain Goodwill Alliance
BNB improved on-chain trading and integrity by creating a community program called 'Goodwill Alliance'.
One of the main or first goals were to eliminate MEV attacks within the BNB ecosystem.
Since this implementation, the average daily volume of sandwich attack transactions on BSC dropped by more than 400%
â¥ TST Token Phenomenon
The â€œTestâ€ token (TST) which was originally designed as a tutorial token for the BNB Chain meme coin launchpad contributed to the ecosystem fee revenue.
The token went as high as $500M market cap, signalling the advent of the BNB meme szn.
â¥

's dog '$BROCCOLI'?

One of these meme coins, saw its market cap soar to over $200 million.
The surge in meme coin trading volume drove PancakeSwap, BNB Chainâ€™s decentralized exchange, to outperform all decentralized exchanges in trading volume, reaching over $15.9 billion on Feb. 13.
â¥ The Four Meme Platform
The meme culture boom in the BNB Chain ecosystem began with the emergence of the Fourmeme platform. Data from Dune reveals that over 200K unique users have engaged with Fourmeme this month alone.
â¥
@cz_binance
's bullposting skill
Changpeng Zhaoâ€™s CZâ€™s frequent updates, strategic bullposting, and engagement with the community can be thanked for piloting investors choice to the black 'n' yellow chain.
There's so much to be excited about on the BNB ecosystem.

is a lesson to take home from this post.
